Author: danielha
Title: My.Netscape Being Re-Born as Web 2.0 Personalized Homepage

Author: danielha
Content: I give this a whirl when they launched. I wasn't too intrigued from the get-go. But I started adding my immediate family tree and, days later, I noticed it grew from my additions -- my dad joined the site (from the email I gave them) and contributed! I felt they had that subtle something when I noticed the broad appeal.

Author: danielha
Content:
There's a lot of industry veterans that I would love to work with.

But as far as a co-founder goes, I'm happy with my current one. We have a great working relationship and we're good friends -- plus our skills compliment each other.
